<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,user-scalable=0">
    <title>Title</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/common.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/swiper.min.css">
    <script src="js/swiper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="js/jquery-1.11.3.min.js"></script>
    <script src="js/jquery.Spinner.js"></script>
    <script>
        $(function(){
            $(".Spinner").Spinner({value:"1", min:1, len:3, max:"1000"});
        });
    </script>
    <style>
        .detail01{
            border-bottom:0.1rem solid #eef4fb;
        }
        .detail01 .pic{
            height:1.8rem;
            width:2.25rem;
        }
        .detail01 .nr{
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: left;
        }
        .detail01 .nr span{
            margin:0 !important;
            line-height:160% !important;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="Body">
        <div id="Header">
            <header class="flex">
                <div class="logo"><img src="http://www.brachysolution.com/res/Home/structure/14112579.png" /></div>
                <div class="head-r flex">
                    <div class="search"></div>
                    <nav>
                        <em></em>
                    </nav>
                </div>
            </header>
        </div>
        <div id="Content">
            <div class="detail01 flex">
                <span class="pic flex">
                    <img src="http://www.brachysolution.com/res/Home/structure/19061406.png" />
                </span>
                <span class="nr flex">
                    <span class="tit">碘125粒子</span>
                    <span class="version"><em>商品编号</em>LDR1102</span>
                    <span class="tit" style="margin:0.2rem 0rem;color:#df6c0a">￥2000</span>

                </span>
            </div>

            <div class="detail02 flex">
                <div class="p flex">
                    <span class="sp1">选择医院</span>
                    <select>
                        <option>郑大一附院</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                <div class="p flex">
                    <span class="sp1">厂　　商</span>
                    <select>
                        <option>君安</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                <div class="p flex">
                    <span class="sp1">粒子活度</span>
                    <em class="flex">
                        <i>0.3-0.8 mCi</i>
                        <i>0.3-0.8 mCi</i>
                        <i>0.3-0.8 mCi</i>
                        <input type="text" placeholder="输入粒子活度" />
                    </em>
                </div>
                <div class="p flex">
                    <span class="sp1">购买数量</span>
                    <div class="Spinner"></div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="detail03 flex">
                <span class="info">
                    <p style="font-size:0.2rem;color:#df6c0a" class="p1">法定工作日8:30至16:30处理订单并安排发货(非法定假日的周六将在8:30至14:30处理订单并安排发货)，否则将顺延至下一工作区间处理。遇特殊节假日，将在网站首页通知接受订单及发货时间；</p>
                </span>
            </div>

            <div class="detail04 flex">
                <input type="submit" value="立即购买" class="but1" />
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
<script>
    $(function () {
        $("em.flex i").click(function () {
            $(this).addClass('cur').siblings("i").removeClass("cur");
        });

    })
</script>
</body>
</html>